    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先创建根节点。用mindmap语法，根节点标记为root，显示文本设为HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目前先保持简洁，这个思维导图作为框架起点，后续我们会逐步添加影像分析模块、病理识别模块这些子节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，当前版本只保留根节点HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，为后续模块扩展预留结构。我确认一下，根节点的括号格式需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "格式上没问题，方括号包裹HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine即可。另外确认一下，mindmap的根节点语法是root[]对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
